[normal] 
[normal]F
[normal]unctioning market and food supply chain
[normal].
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Re
[normal]form to be pursued equally across the EU and by major global players like the US
[normal]A
[normal]. 
[normal]As long as British farmers continue to compete within the European single market, it is important that we remain part of a common policy framework for agriculture and that English farmers are treated fairly within that framework. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]full
[normal] decoupling of direct support payments
[normal].
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]the
[normal] move towards the area based payments system
[normal].
[normal]•
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Government’s use of national modulation.  
